{{create=(ch:=character()).create_cc_nx((cc:="Robe of Stars"), 0, 6, 'none', 'bubble')}}{{re,r,a,c='&1&'.lower() in 'recharge',vroll('1d6'),'&1&'.lower() in 'astral',combat()}}{{v=ch.get_cc(cc)>0 and not (re or a)}}{{f'''embed -title "{name} looks at their robe as the sun sets." -desc "{r} star{'' if r.total<2 else 's'} reappeared on your robe tonight!" ''' if re else [f'''embed -title "{name} uses the {cc} to {'enter the Astral Plane!' if c and c.me and not c.me.get_effect(cc) else 'leave the Astral Plane!' if c and c.me else 'Plane Shift!'}" -desc "While you wear the robe, you can use an action to enter the Astral Plane along with everything you are wearing and carrying. You remain there until you use an action to return to the plane you were on. You reappear in the last space you occupied, or if that space is occupied, the nearest unoccupied space." -f """{f"Effect|{cc}: in the Astral plane" if c and c.me and not c.me.get_effect(cc) else f"Warning:|You are now leaving the Astral Plane." if c and c.me else 'Effect|Plane Shift - tracking not avaliable outside init.'}""" ''', (c.me.add_effect(cc+": in the Astral Plane") if not c.me.get_effect(cc) else c.me.remove_effect(cc)) if c and c.me else ''][0] if a else '''cast "magic missile" &*& -i -phrase "By tearing a star from their robe!"''' if v else f'''embed -title "All the stars are gone from the {cc}!" '''}}
{{ch.mod_cc(cc, -1) if v else ch.mod_cc(cc, +int(r.total)) if re else ''}}
-f "Robe of Stars|This dark blue robe is embroidered with six stars, located on the robe's upper front portion, are particularly large. While wearing this robe, you can use an action to pull off one of the stars and use it to cast magic missile as a 5th-level spell. Daily at dusk, 1d6 removed stars reappear on the robe."
-f "{{cc}}{{" (-1)" if v else f' (+{r.total})' if re else ''}}|{{ch.cc_str(cc)}}"
-footer "{{ctx.prefix+ctx.alias}} [target and -rr 7] or [targets] / {{ctx.prefix+ctx.alias}} recharge / {{ctx.prefix+ctx.alias}} astral"
-thumb https://media-waterdeep.cursecdn.com/avatars/thumbnails/7/380/315/315/636284763972311694.jpeg
